<svg viewBox="0 0 700 460" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
<text x="20" y="26" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Bitcoin 2021–2022 — The Pattern's Target Was Right, the Path Was Wrong</text>
<text x="20" y="46" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Head-and-shoulders measured target (~$15K) vs. the three events that actually made the low</text>
<line x1="60" y1="400" x2="670" y2="400" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,.15)"/>
